{
  "stem": "27507.11",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And on 14th of September, somebody woke me up early in the morning and we looked out of the door early in the morning, still hiding, and we saw that on the street, which was about a couple of hundred meters to the left-- to the right, sorry-- there were-- was-- German army was-- was going down.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they all were walking in-- not in any organized way, but they were walking in groups, but they were walking and walking and walking, and some cars and some armored cars.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were-- and they walked and walked for a long time, and then they disappeared.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then there was peace and quiet and there was nobody there for a while.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "For an hour or two hours, there was nobody there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we couldn't even believe that the Germans went.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, they went there, and we didn't know exactly where they were, but they went there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was the way to the north.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They must have gone to the bridge, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There were still some-- must have been some pontoon bridge, because the bridges, they sprang-- they exploded the big bridges on the Vistula.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And few hours later, the Russians appeared.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There were some Russians.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sorry?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Soldiers, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Soldiers appeared suddenly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We saw again soldiers, Russian soldiers, coming.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we didn't dare to go out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then the soldiers appeared all over the terrain.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And some soldiers came to our door, and we-- my father could speak Russian so he spoke to them, but I think he didn't say exactly who we were.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were friendly.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
